  ->  Sort  (cost=418.80..420.29 rows=599 width=50) (actual time=18.192..18.192 rows=5 loops=1)
        Sort Key: (count(*)) DESC
        Sort Method: top-N heapsort  Memory: 25kB
        ->  HashAggregate  (cost=402.86..408.85 rows=599 width=50) (actual time=17.975..18.048 rows=599 loops=1)
              Group By Key: customer_id
              ->  Partition Iterator  (cost=0.00..282.49 rows=16049 width=10) (actual time=0.022..7.006 rows=16049 loops=1)
                    Iterations: 7
                    ->  Partitioned Seq Scan on payment  (cost=0.00..282.49 rows=16049 width=10) (actual time=0.061..2.417 rows=16049 loops=7)
                          Selected Partitions:  1..7
